{"tha-ap402:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap402:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap402:0.3":"Ajitattheraapadana ","tha-ap402:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap402:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap402:1.3":"Ajjhogahetva himavantam, ","tha-ap402:1.4":"nisidi lokanayako. ","tha-ap402:2.1":"Naham addakkhim sambuddham, ","tha-ap402:2.2":"Napi saddam sunomaham; ","tha-ap402:2.3":"Mama bhakkham gavesanto, ","tha-ap402:2.4":"Ahindami vane aham. ","tha-ap402:3.1":"Tatthaddassasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap402:3.2":"dvattimsavaralakkhanam; ","tha-ap402:3.3":"Disvana vittimapajjim, ","tha-ap402:3.4":"satto ko namayam bhave. ","tha-ap402:4.1":"Lakkhanani viloketva, ","tha-ap402:4.2":"mama vijjam anussarim; ","tha-ap402:4.3":"Sutanhi metam vuddhanam, ","tha-ap402:4.4":"panditanam subhasitam. ","tha-ap402:5.1":"Tesam yatha tam vacanam, ","tha-ap402:5.2":"ayam buddho bhavissati; ","tha-ap402:5.3":"Yannunaham sakkareyyam, ","tha-ap402:5.4":"gatim me sodhayissati. ","tha-ap402:6.1":"Khippam assamamagantva, ","tha-ap402:6.2":"madhutelam gahim aham; ","tha-ap402:6.3":"Kolambakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap402:6.4":"upagacchim vinayakam. ","tha-ap402:7.1":"Tidandake gahetvana, ","tha-ap402:7.2":"abbhokase thapesaham; ","tha-ap402:7.3":"Padipam pajjalitvana, ","tha-ap402:7.4":"atthakkhattum avandaham. ","tha-ap402:8.1":"Sattarattindivam buddho, ","tha-ap402:8.2":"nisidi purisuttamo; ","tha-ap402:8.3":"Tato ratya vivasane, ","tha-ap402:8.4":"vutthasi lokanayako. ","tha-ap402:9.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap402:9.2":"sabbarattindivam aham; ","tha-ap402:9.3":"Dipam buddhassa padasim, ","tha-ap402:9.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap402:10.1":"Sabbe vana gandhamaya, ","tha-ap402:10.2":"Pabbate gandhamadane; ","tha-ap402:10.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap402:10.4":"Agacchum buddhasantikam. ","tha-ap402:11.1":"Ye keci pupphagandhase, ","tha-ap402:11.2":"pupphita dharaniruha; ","tha-ap402:11.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap402:11.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap402:12.1":"Yavata himavantamhi, ","tha-ap402:12.2":"naga ca garula ubho; ","tha-ap402:12.3":"Dhammanca sotukama te, ","tha-ap402:12.4":"agacchum buddhasantikam. ","tha-ap402:13.1":"Devalo nama samano, ","tha-ap402:13.2":"buddhassa aggasavako; ","tha-ap402:13.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap402:13.4":"buddhasantikupagami. ","tha-ap402:14.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap402:14.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap402:14.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap402:14.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap402:15.1":"‘Yo me dipam padipesi, ","tha-ap402:15.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap402:15.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap402:15.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap402:16.1":"Satthi kappasahassani, ","tha-ap402:16.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap402:16.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap402:16.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap402:17.1":"Solasamam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap402:18.1":"Chattimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap402:18.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap402:18.3":"Pathaviyam sattasatam, ","tha-ap402:18.4":"vipulam rajjam karissati. ","tha-ap402:19.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap402:19.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap402:19.3":"Imina dipadanena, ","tha-ap402:19.4":"dibbacakkhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap402:20.1":"Samantato atthakosam, ","tha-ap402:20.2":"passissati ayam sada; ","tha-ap402:20.3":"Devaloka cavantassa, ","tha-ap402:20.4":"nibbattantassa jantuno. ","tha-ap402:21.1":"Diva va yadi va rattim, ","tha-ap402:21.2":"padipam dharayissati; ","tha-ap402:21.3":"Jayamanassa sattassa, ","tha-ap402:21.4":"punnakammasamangino. ","tha-ap402:22.1":"Yavata nagaram asi, ","tha-ap402:22.2":"tavata jotayissati; ","tha-ap402:22.3":"Upapajjati yam yonim, ","tha-ap402:22.4":"devattam atha manusam. ","tha-ap402:23.1":"Asseva dipadanassa, ","tha-ap402:23.2":"atthadipaphalena hi; ","tha-ap402:23.3":"Na jayissantimam jantu, ","tha-ap402:23.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap402:24.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap402:24.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap402:24.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap402:24.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap402:25.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap402:25.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap402:25.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap402:25.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap402:26.1":"Tosayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap402:26.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap402:26.3":"Ajito nama namena, ","tha-ap402:26.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap402:27.1":"Satthi kappasahassani, ","tha-ap402:27.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap402:27.3":"Tatrapi me dipasatam, ","tha-ap402:27.4":"jotate niccakalikam. ","tha-ap402:28.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap402:28.2":"niddhavanti pabha mama; ","tha-ap402:28.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap402:28.4":"bhiyyo hasam janesaham. ","tha-ap402:29.1":"Tusitaham cavitvana, ","tha-ap402:29.2":"okkamim matukucchiyam; ","tha-ap402:29.3":"Jayamanassa santassa, ","tha-ap402:29.4":"aloko vipulo ahu. ","tha-ap402:30.1":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap402:30.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap402:30.3":"Bavarim upasankamma, ","tha-ap402:30.4":"sissattam ajjhupagamim. ","tha-ap402:31.1":"Himavante vasantoham, ","tha-ap402:31.2":"assosim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap402:31.3":"Uttamattham gavesanto, ","tha-ap402:31.4":"upagacchim vinayakam. ","tha-ap402:32.1":"Danto buddho dametavi, ","tha-ap402:32.2":"oghatinno nirupadhi; ","tha-ap402:32.3":"Nibbanam kathayi buddho, ","tha-ap402:32.4":"sabbadukkhappamocanam. ","tha-ap402:33.1":"Tam me agamanam siddham, ","tha-ap402:33.2":"tositoham mahamunim; ","tha-ap402:33.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap402:33.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap402:34.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap402:34.2":"yam dipamadadim tada; ","tha-ap402:34.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap402:34.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap402:35.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap402:35.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap402:35.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap402:36.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap402:36.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap402:36.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap402:37.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap402:37.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap402:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap402:38.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ajito thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap402:39.1":"Ajitattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap402:39.2":"Pilindavacchavaggo cattalisamo. ","tha-ap402:40.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap402:41.1":"Pilindavaccho selo ca, ","tha-ap402:41.2":"sabbakitti madhundado; ","tha-ap402:41.3":"Kutagari bakulo ca, ","tha-ap402:41.4":"giri salalasavhayo. ","tha-ap402:42.1":"Sabbado ajito ceva, ","tha-ap402:42.2":"gathayo ganita iha; ","tha-ap402:42.3":"Satani panca gathanam, ","tha-ap402:42.4":"visati ca taduttariti. ","tha-ap402:43.1":"Atha vagguddanam ","tha-ap402:44.1":"Padumarakkhado ceva, ","tha-ap402:44.2":"uma gandhodakena ca; ","tha-ap402:44.3":"Ekapadma saddasanni, ","tha-ap402:44.4":"mandaram bodhivandako. ","tha-ap402:45.1":"Avatanca pilindi ca, ","tha-ap402:45.2":"gathayo ganita iha; ","tha-ap402:45.3":"Catusattati gathayo, ","tha-ap402:45.4":"ekadasa satani ca. ","tha-ap402:46.1":"Padumavaggadasakam. ","tha-ap402:47.1":"Catutthasatakam samattam. "}